    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="32203878">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-32203878" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-32203878" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="32203878">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/shanshuiyouyan/">山水幽燕</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2008-02-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">从情报工作做起到成为学术专家，而自己的工作由积累信息到积累知识，费正清这点让人印象深刻</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="102734001">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-102734001" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-102734001" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="102734001">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yuancheng/">Bazinga</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2009-03-10</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">历史是无法还原的，后来者只有管中窥豹，这本书好在它对管口的大小拿捏得十分到位，该写的都写了，又点到为止。于我而言，最棒的地方是它重燃了我被中学课本扑灭的对历史的兴趣。两点不足一是句子太零散，转呈不自然；二是可能因翻译的缘故，语言也不够通畅。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

